metadata.name: STAR PEPE
metadata.description: For the love of PEPE. Putting the Fun back into the crypto space and bringing people together. Frogs are a symbol of prosperity & Good Luck. PEPE the meme is a legend and part of pop culture. The community inspired me to write this song, I feel the passion, excitement and fun. To the Moon or down to ZERO, we love PEPE , there's no losing. We made new friends, we made art, we're sharing our passion for crypto and web3. Cheers to the PEPE Community and long live the King Of Memes ;)
